rComments: Although the course being heavy in terms of content, the concepts are fun to learn about and not too complicated to understand. However, her tests are very tough as she wants specific answers. No need to attend lectures since all she does is read off the lecture slides. Her availability is only through appointments and she never replies to emails.

Attending lectures is pointless, unless you show up to record. She talks a mile an hour and doesn't give any time to write notes. The marking is incredibly tough, be ready to memorize everything and be expected to master her material as she wants lots of detail. Besides being a terrible lecturer, she does seem to be passionate about her work
Easy class to do well since no exams, only presentations Prof is a bit picky with what she wants, but gives good marks she's passionate about her research
